<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="es">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>StaySmart Experiences — Tours y Actividades</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://www.staysmartrealty.com">
    <style>
        * { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif; }

        body {
            background: radial-gradient(circle at 50% 30%, #102a45 0%, #050c14 70%);
            color: #ffffff;
            min-height: 100vh;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            overflow-x: hidden;
            position: relative;
        }

        body::before {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            top: 0; left: 0; right: 0; bottom: 0;
            background: radial-gradient(rgba(0,242,254,0.05) 2px, transparent 4px), radial-gradient(rgba(255,255,255,0.02) 1px, transparent 3px);
            background-size: 80px 80px, 40px 40px;
            background-position: 0 0, 20px 20px;
            z-index: 0;
            pointer-events: none;
        }

        .glow-bg {
            position: absolute; top: 15%; left: 50%;
            transform: translate(-50%,-50%);
            width: 500px; height: 250px;
            background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(0,242,254,0.12) 0%, transparent 70%);
            z-index: 0; pointer-events: none;
        }

        header {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
            padding: 25px 50px;
            position: relative;
            z-index: 10;
            width: 100%;
            background: rgba(5, 12, 20, 0.3);
            backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
            border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.03);
        }

        .back-link {
            color: rgba(255,255,255,0.6);
            text-decoration: none;
            font-size: 0.85rem;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 1.5px;
            transition: all 0.3s;
        }
        .back-link:hover { color: #00f2fe; text-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0,242,254,0.5); }

        .main-content {
            flex: 1;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            padding: 40px 20px;
            z-index: 5;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .brand-logo-area {
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            align-items: center;
            margin-bottom: 40px;
        }

        .brand-logo-area img { width: 90px; margin-bottom: 15px; }

        h1 {
            font-size: 2.2rem;
            letter-spacing: 1px;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #00f2fe 0%, #4facfe 100%);
            -webkit-background-clip: text;
            background-clip: text;
            -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
        }

        .exp-desc {
            max-width: 600px;
            color: rgba(255,255,255,0.65);
            line-height: 1.7;
            margin-bottom: 40px;
            font-size: 1rem;
        }

        .destinos-grid {
            display: flex;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            justify-content: center;
            gap: 12px;
            max-width: 800px;
            margin-bottom: 45px;
        }

        .destino-tag {
            background: rgba(255,255,255,0.04);
            border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.1);
            border-radius: 30px;
            padding: 8px 18px;
            font-size: 0.85rem;
            color: rgba(255,255,255,0.7);
        }

        .action-btn {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #00f2fe 0%, #4facfe 100%);
            color: #050c14;
            border: none;
            padding: 16px 34px;
            border-radius: 6px;
            font-weight: bold;
            font-size: 1rem;
            cursor: pointer;
            text-decoration: none;
            transition: all 0.3s;
            display: inline-block;
        }

        .action-btn:hover {
            transform: scale(1.03);
            box-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(0,242,254,0.4);
        }

        .note {
            margin-top: 20px;
            font-size: 0.8rem;
            color: rgba(255,255,255,0.35);
            max-width: 500px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <div class="glow-bg"></div>

    <header>
        <a href="index.html" class="back-link">&larr; Volver a StaySmart</a>
    </header>

    <div class="main-content">
        <div class="brand-logo-area">
            <img src="Logo-staysmart.png" alt="StaySmart Logo">
        </div>

        <h1>Descubre Experiencias de Viaje</h1>
        <p class="exp-desc">
            Tours, atracciones y actividades imperdibles en los destinos más emocionantes del mundo:
            Japón, Corea, Taiwán, Hong Kong, China, el Sudeste Asiático, Europa y Estados Unidos.
        </p>

        <div class="destinos-grid">
            <span class="destino-tag">Tokyo Disney Resort</span>
            <span class="destino-tag">Universal Studios Japan</span>
            <span class="destino-tag">Shibuya Sky</span>
            <span class="destino-tag">Nami Island</span>
            <span class="destino-tag">Everland</span>
            <span class="destino-tag">Taipei 101</span>
            <span class="destino-tag">Hong Kong Disneyland</span>
            <span class="destino-tag">Bangkok · Bali · Singapore</span>
            <span class="destino-tag">Eiffel Tower · Louvre</span>
            <span class="destino-tag">Grand Canyon · Broadway</span>
        </div>

        <div style="display:flex; gap:20px; flex-wrap:wrap; justify-content:center;">
            <a href="https://kkday.tpk.lv/Q8FfqsuJ" id="kkday-link" class="action-btn" target="_blank" rel="noopener">
                Explorar Experiencias con KKday
            </a>
            <a href="https://klook.tpk.lv/2LiCytsS" id="klook-link" class="action-btn" target="_blank" rel="noopener">
                Explorar Experiencias con Klook
            </a>
        </div>

        <p class="note">Al hacer clic entrarás a la plataforma correspondiente, donde podrás elegir tu destino, fecha y reservar directamente.</p>
    </div>

</body>
</html>
